{"tid":877351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科學家發現「超巨型400歲格陵蘭鯊魚」","createTime":"2018-10-26T09:35:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T09:57:38.000Z","uid":54373,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c9574865531212133a35179674287ed8a1266944","tid":877351,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.news18nepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18nepal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F1800.jpg&h=181f5334&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你能想像世界上某個角落，有隻生物默默的活了400年，活過人類史上一代又一代的變遷。科學家發現一隻史上最長壽的雌性格陵蘭鯊魚 (Greenland sharks) ，又名小頭睡鯊。年齡超過過去211歲弓頭鯨的長壽紀錄，成為地球上最長壽的脊椎動物！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.news18nepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1-188.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18nepal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F1-188.jpg&h=cfec3638&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n根據外媒報導，格陵蘭鯊大約是出生在英國國王詹姆士一世 (1603年3月24日-1625年3月27日) 的統治期間，不僅度過英國的朝代更迭，更是經歷過兩次世界大戰。格陵蘭鯊擁有灰色、豐腴的身體，身長長達5公尺，是目前世界上最大的肉食動物之一。據科學家研究，格陵蘭鯊平均一年生長不到一公分，可見格陵蘭鯊在世上活了多久。<br />\n <br />\n格陵蘭鯊目前的年紀是科學家大約推算，來自冰島大學的鯊魚專家史蒂芬 ‧ 坎帕納 (Steven Campana) 表示：「這幾年，生物學家一直試圖確定這隻格陵蘭鯊魚的年齡，但沒有成功。鑑於這條鯊魚是北極水域中食物鏈頂端，我們不確定鯊魚是活了20年，還是1000年，但這一切都很令人難以置信。」透過格陵蘭鯊的研究，可以幫助生物學家做出鯊魚平均壽命的推斷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.news18nepal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/2-164.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18nepal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F2-164.jpg&h=271f2a15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為了確定鯊魚的年齡，科學家們使用了許多方法，其中包括檢查鯊魚眼中的晶狀體，晶狀體是隨著時間積累的蛋白質組成的，當鯊魚在媽媽的子宮內發育時，蛋白質會位於晶狀體的中心。科學家表示，只要能計算出這些蛋白質生長時間，便可以估算出鯊魚的年齡。"},{"pid":"a20583d7a30d805f9bf193ab5de8344cb46e5538","tid":877351,"uid":68220,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:39:18.000Z","msg":"唔好搞佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n畀支國人知道咗就冇好下場"},{"pid":"ab3816af887ab86424502d7f8887e49103cd4441","tid":877351,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82d23cd62c2691ef09a239a9b773df6620cf4ee","tid":877351,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a20583d7a30d805f9bf193ab5de8344cb46e5538","tid":877351,"uid":68220,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:39:18.000Z","msg":"唔好搞佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n畀支國人知道咗就冇好下場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:42:28.000Z","msg":"魚翅拍賣一定好價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350d293b336978891b5d461ab5f8412ee571619e","tid":877351,"uid":202354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a20583d7a30d805f9bf193ab5de8344cb46e5538","tid":877351,"uid":68220,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:39:18.000Z","msg":"唔好搞佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n畀支國人知道咗就冇好下場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:42:53.000Z","msg":"格陵蘭人會殺呢種鯊魚，可能死係格陵蘭人手上"},{"pid":"3d4e45c1cd90ae4b2d72f8172e50f8ffbf96f2c1","tid":877351,"uid":38131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:43:09.000Z","msg":"咁老啲細胞都未死哂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1011e36c00cf87216828dd0f63ac77640bed39df","tid":877351,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:44:51.000Z","msg":"支那人： 唔, 古早味"},{"pid":"819683a888e32d4ca5c550104bd59c7823c4a07b","tid":877351,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3d4e45c1cd90ae4b2d72f8172e50f8ffbf96f2c1","tid":877351,"uid":38131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:43:09.000Z","msg":"咁老啲細胞都未死哂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:45:15.000Z","msg":"150歲後先做真男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n格陵蘭鯊魚壽命可達400歲，是地球上已知最長壽的脊椎動物，其長壽主因是，這種動物的生長速度非常慢，大約每年只長1公分，在150歲時性發育才達成熟階段。依放射性碳定年技術測得資料推算，格陵蘭鯊魚的平均年齡大約為272歲，最長壽命肯定超過400歲。科學家說，<span style=\"color: red;\">牠們長壽的重要因素就是「慢慢長」加上「慢慢活」。</span>"},{"pid":"95d6498883b05ec5f5c3ee676491e362e54c4dba","tid":877351,"uid":20428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:47:41.000Z","msg":"即係有幾大條"},{"pid":"ff2c153332542a64443abca15d2d787e66b6afbf","tid":877351,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:48:03.000Z","msg":"魚翅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b9aaf62f80151735399bdecf91caaf24b776f9","tid":877351,"uid":68220,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"819683a888e32d4ca5c550104bd59c7823c4a07b","tid":877351,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3d4e45c1cd90ae4b2d72f8172e50f8ffbf96f2c1","tid":877351,"uid":38131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:43:09.000Z","msg":"咁老啲細胞都未死哂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:45:15.000Z","msg":"150歲後先做真男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n格陵蘭鯊魚壽命可達400歲，是地球上已知最長壽的脊椎動物，其長壽主因是，這種動物的生長速度非常慢，大約每年只長1公分，在150歲時性發育才達成熟階段。依放射性碳定年技術測得資料推算，格陵蘭鯊魚的平均年齡大約為272歲，最長壽命肯定超過400歲。科學家說，<span style=\"color: red;\">牠們長壽的重要因素就是「慢慢長」加上「慢慢活」。</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:55:26.000Z","msg":"150歲仲係處<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有動物慘過我了 好開心"},{"pid":"c9d532d0a44a3f5312bca6eaae6e3f885fa63f02","tid":877351,"uid":52006,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:57:38.000Z","msg":"150歲先識扑野, 咁多年點捱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}